item.title: Vanished From Scandalous Catholic College Campus: Where Is Joshua Guimond?
item.description: Joshua Guimond was a 20-year-old college student with a bright future in politics ahead of him. So on November 10th, 2002, when he vanished from a dorm party on the St. John’s University campus, everyone who knew him was shocked. Searches turned up no sign of Josh, and he hasn’t been seen since. Secrets uncovered on Josh’s computer hard drive, and a sex abuse scandal at the nearby monastery, may hold the key to solving Josh’s disappearance. Feed: https://audioboom.com/channels/5011925.rss
